name: $10 Gift Certificate to Collective Clothing
description:
Ideas:
1. Buy one for yourself.
2. Buy one for a friend.
3. Buy one for an enemy.
4. Makes a great Stocking Stuffer!
5. Use in store or online!
6. Buy one for every member of your family and staff.
7. Buy one and bury it in the ground and see who finds it.

name: Vintage Police T-shirt
description:
Possibly the coolest vintage Police Shirt you will find online and with a cool back story too.  We found these gems and the other t-shirts that are on our site at a Gas Station turned print shop in a small town in Illinois.  The Print shop had them around as an inheritance from their mom that use to travel with the carnival and sell them from the mid 70's to early 80's.  These shirts have an RN# on the tag with the brand name "Fantasy A & G" and are new with a worn in look. They have been washed. Please inquire about what sizes we have available.  If you have any questions feel free to email us at: collectiveclothing@rocketmail.com
You can view the entire catalogue at http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.10150186797074547.328188.76533394546&type=1

Make sure to like us at facebook.com/collectiveclothing

Thanks for looking!
